<HEADLINE> AP Top News at 1 a.m. EDT  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Saturdday, Aug. 12, 2000
</P>
<SUBHEAD>
Buchanan Wins Reform Party Nod
</SUBHEAD>
