attended Friday's hearing in a wheelchair.
</P>
<P>
   Her husband, Richard Flores, 42; their sons, Richard Jr., 17,
and Matthew, 10, and daughter, Sylvia, 13, were killed as they
slept. Two of the couple's other daughters were unharmed.
