<HEADLINE> No winner, jackpot increases to $17 million for Tuesday drawing  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	   ATLANTA (AP) - The jackpot in the multistate Big Game lottery
drawing has grown to $17 million.
</P>
<P>
   None of the tickets sold for Friday's $13 million drawing
matched all five lotto numbers and the Big Money Ball. The next
drawing will be Tuesday, Aug. 15.
</P>
<P>
