an interview to Playboy magazine in which he criticized organized religion. His
comments came yesterday during a closed meeting with a CIA leadership group in a
Capitol hearing room. Reporters were barred, but a microphone was left on and
WCCO-TV taped the session. In the November Playboy issue, Ventura ignited a
firestorm by saying organized religion was ''a sham and a crutch for weak-minded
people who need strength in numbers. It tells people to go out and stick their
noses in other people's business.''
</P>
